{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>某个局域网内有n(n≤100)台计算机，由于搭建局域网时工作人员的疏忽，现在局域网内的连接形成了回路，我们知道如果局域网形成回路那么数据将不停的在回路内传输，造成网络卡的现象。因为连接计算机的网线本身不同，所以有一些连线不是很畅通，我们用f(i,j)表示i,j之间连接的畅通程度(f(i,j)≤1000)，f(i,j)值越小表示i,j之间连接越通畅，f(i,j)为0表示i,j之间无网线连接。现在我们需要解决回路问题，我们将除去一些连线，使得网络中没有回路，并且被除去网线的Σf(i,j)最大，请求出这个最大值。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"局域网 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>一个正整数，Σf(i,j)的最大值。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行两个正整数n k<p><p>接下来的k行每行三个正整数i j m表示i,j两台计算机之间有网线联通，通畅程度为m。<p>","examples":"<input>5 5\n1 2 8\n1 3 1\n1 5 3\n2 4 5\n3 4 2\n\n</input><output>8\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1391","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}